## 🎯 **OPERATIONAL BEST PRACTICES**

### **Code Implementation**

- Follow established coding standards
- Write clean, readable, maintainable code
- Use meaningful variable and function names
- Add appropriate comments and documentation
- Implement error handling and validation

### **Testing Strategy**

- Write tests before or alongside implementation
- Test edge cases and error conditions
- Validate against requirements and specifications
- Use automated testing when possible
- Document test results and issues

### **Progress Management**

- Update todos regularly and accurately
- Track time spent on tasks
- Identify and resolve blockers quickly
- Communicate status and issues promptly
- Maintain clear handoff documentation

